		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You place your hands on the ground, and begin describing your favorite food and drink. Gallons of plain water and pounds of a nourishing but tasteless and bland-looking imitation of your favorite dish appears on the ground near you.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>Create 45 pounds of food and 30 gallons of water on the ground or in containers within range. This is enough to sustain up to fifteen small/medium humanoids or five large creatures for 24 hours.</p></li><li><p>The food is bland but nourishing, and spoils rapidly if uneaten after 24 hours. The water is clean.</p></li></ul>",
